common_examples.text: TikTok is THE destination for mobile videos.
On TikTok, short-form videos are exciting, spontaneous, and genuine.
Whether you’re a sports fanatic, a pet enthusiast, or just looking for a laugh, there’s something for everyone on TikTok.
All you have to do is watch, engage with what you like, skip what you don’t, and you’ll find an endless stream of short videos that feel personalized just for you.

entities.value: watch, engage with what you like
find an endless stream of short videos

common_examples.text: From your morning coffee to your afternoon errands, TikTok has the videos that are guaranteed to make your day.
We make it easy for you to discover and create your own original videos by providing easy-to-use tools to view and capture your daily moments.

entities.value: discover and create your own original videos
view and capture your daily moments

common_examples.text: Take your videos to the next level with special effects, filters, music, and more.

entities.value: Take your videos to the next level
